---

<section
  id="expectations"
  class="bg-black text-white w-screen flex flex-col justify-between py-8"
>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col justify-between items-center xl:flex-row xl:justify-between w-full px-4 xl:px-24"
  >
    <!-- Texto a la izquierda -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center xl:items-start xl:w-1/2 xl:pr-8 mb-4"
    >
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center xl:text-left font-poppins tracking-wide">
        ¿Qué ofrecemos?
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 w-full">

        <!-- Cuidamos de ti -->
        <details class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 via-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4 group">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer select-none font-semibold text-2xl text-white flex items-center justify-between mb-2 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:text-yellow-300"
          >
            <span>Cuidamos de ti</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-0 overflow-hidden group-open:max-h-96 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-80 rounded-lg p-2">
            <p class="text-lg mt-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Hacemos todo lo que está en nuestras manos para que poco a poco
              adhieras el deporte a tu vida de una manera sana y sostenible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Marcamos objetivos -->
        <details class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 via-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4 group">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer select-none font-semibold text-2xl text-white flex items-center justify-between mb-2 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:text-yellow-300"
          >
            <span>Marcamos objetivos</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-0 overflow-hidden group-open:max-h-96 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-80 rounded-lg p-2">
            <p class="text-lg mt-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              En nuestras programaciones avanzamos día a día para mejorar y
              obtener objetivos perceptibles y de calidad.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Tu hora del día -->
        <details class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-800 via-gray-700 to-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-4 group">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer select-none font-semibold text-2xl text-white flex items-center justify-between mb-2 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:text-yellow-300"
          >
            <span>Tu hora del día</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-0 overflow-hidden group-open:max-h-96 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-80 rounded-lg p-2">
            <p class="text-lg mt-2 leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Que el tiempo que estés con nosotros sea un momento en el que
              disfrutes con el grupo, adquieras confianza y sientas el apoyo de
              nuestros entrenadores y comunidad.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Imagen a la derecha -->
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center xl:w-1/2 xl:pl-8 mt-4 xl:mt-0">
      <img
        class="w-full h-auto object-contain rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        src="./fotoprincipal.jpg"
        alt="Equipo Best Studio"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
